extends layout

block content
  h1 Book Database Application
  p Welcome to the Book RESTful API
  
  h2 Web Views
  ul
    li 
      a(href="/books") View All Books
    li 
      a(href="/grid") Grid Demo
    li 
      a(href="/randomitem") Random Item Picker
  
  h2 RESTful API Endpoints
  p Base URL: /api
  
  h3 Available Operations:
  ul
    li 
      strong GET /api/books 
      | - Get all books
    li 
      strong GET /api/books/:id 
      | - Get a specific book by ID
    li 
      strong POST /api/books 
      | - Create a new book
    li 
      strong PUT /api/books/:id 
      | - Update a book by ID
    li 
      strong DELETE /api/books/:id 
      | - Delete a book by ID
  
  p 
    em Use tools like Postman, Thunder Client, or curl to test the API endpoints.
